.env
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/
# Heavy generated/data dirs — code-only repo (PD 2026-06-04: A/B/C branch test)
data/
assets/bgm/
assets/branding/
*.mp4
*.mov
*.heic
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
# Character reference images are load-bearing pipeline assets (they anchor the pets'
# appearance in AV still-gen). Version-control them so they deploy to the VM — the
# blanket *.png ignore left them off the VM, so AV Leo drifted grey/white with no real
# orange anchor (retro: AV0800 2026-07-19). Keep the set the pipeline actually reads.
!assets/character_ref/base_both.png
!assets/character_ref/base_both_clean.png
!assets/character_ref/leo_real.png
!assets/character_ref/ryani_solo.png
!assets/character_ref/ryani_real.png
!assets/character_ref/official_ryani_leo.png
!assets/character_ref/official_ryani_leo_cafe.png
!assets/character_ref/ryani_wink.png
# Prop reference images anchor recurring props (harness, carrier bag) across cuts so they
# don't drift in Seedance ref-mode (retro: AV X5Le 2026-07-20 — Ryani's harness vanished
# mid-episode, Leo's bag changed size). Same version-control-or-it's-not-on-the-VM lesson.
!assets/props/
!assets/props/*.jpg
!assets/props/*.png
youtube/token.json
youtube/client_secret.json
.DS_Store
.env.bak
*.lock
assets/**/*.bak
osxphotos_crash.log
